4:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/26/110329_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F26%2F110329_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e3c58256&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/26/110350_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F26%2F110350_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=f7e41cf3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b8861bd2332e9418afbe5eb8daa60a5604ecf64","tid":572854,"uid":42820,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T03:06:42.000Z","msg":"騰訊而家個價格跟本就係大家亂叫亂炒出黎，<br />\n<br />\n本身佢只係一張廿蚊紙，吹到佢又咩價值連城呀，又咩每年升一倍，係氣氛之下，你地居然用左1000蚊去買左張廿蚊紙。 希望佢升到上2000，3000蚊，但佢事實價值只係一張廿蚊。<br />\n<br />\n咁大戶係個市場打滾咁耐老江湖，一早知道佢既真實價值只係廿蚊，見咁好水當然賣曬去。<br />\n<br />\n而家有d人輸錢啦，輸左唔捨得賣。好天真希望大戶會回心轉意用返1000蚊出黎買返張廿蚊佢。咁佢就可以放貨賺贏班大戶錢啦<br />\n<br />\n騰訊又無息收，長渣黎就算佢廿年後好彩升返，你都係輸曬時間值。<br />\n<br />\n而家匯豐係底位，歷史高位係150，重有成倍上望空間。<br />\n你渣匯豐起碼每年有5厘息，你買100萬都每年有5萬。就算你坐艇，20年後你收息都收左100萬。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊呢?你收到咩?"},{"pid":"0ddfd22d3ffcb4e6f75401ae2786d6ab78c8e684","tid":572854,"uid":81150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T03:14:26.000Z","msg":"走哂了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b746e5531f736a87141fa986a7f25ed5898e78bd","tid":572854,"uid":96970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T03:50:26.000Z","msg":"即刻買左1萬蚊熊 信晒你喇巴打"},{"pid":"01328303568113ffbe1866123b9826a15dc789c4","tid":572854,"uid":67488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T04:02:13.000Z","msg":"期結大升局&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a47620df773acf43d78acbaebc5c734203b2c993","tid":572854,"uid":37130,"like":0,"dislike